verbose_text: There were no significant differences between glucose level of cell only supernatants and all cell seeded decellularized tracheal groups (P = 0.4, P = 0.58, P = 1, P = 0.07, P = 0.06, and P = 1, respectively) and there was significant difference between glucose level of empty trachea sample supernatants and all cell seeded decellularized tracheal groups (P = 0.011, P = 0.012, P = 0.02, P = 0.03, P = 0.03, and P = 0.04, respectively).
